Question 4: answer b: Test cases for component testing are usually derived from component specifications, design specifications, or data models, whereas test cases forsystem testing are usually derived from requirement specifications or use cases
Question 5: answer c: It is possible to perform functional, non-functional and white-box testing at any test level
Question 6: answer c: 1 = component test; 2 = acceptance test; 3 = integration test; 4 = system test
